<h1>Importance of Time Management for Students</h1>

<section>
  <h2>Introduction</h2>
  <p>
    Time management is an important skill for students. It helps them organize their time and complete tasks effectively.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Why Time Management Is Important</h2>
  <p>
    Managing time well allows students to reduce stress, improve academic performance, and balance school with daily life.
  </p>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Tips for Better Time Management</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Create a daily study schedule</li>
    <li>Set clear goals and priorities</li>
    <li>Avoid procrastination</li>
    <li>Take short breaks</li>
  </ul>
</section>

<section>
  <h2>Conclusion</h2>
  <p>
    In conclusion, time management helps students become more successful, confident, and responsible.
  </p>
